data.description: This home is conveniently located only one mile from Downtown Siloam Springs and two blocks from Southside Elementary School. Equipped with three bedrooms (one could be a second living space with wood burning fireplace), two full bathrooms and oversized family room. This carpet-less home has so much potential to make it your own. If the inside was not enough, the large back deck with massive fenced in yard will win you (and your pets/kids) over.  New HVAC in 2020. New water heater in 2019/2020.
